      <h2>Investment Considerations for 2026</h2>
      <p>Space investing involves higher volatility due to technological risks, regulatory changes, and capital intensity. Most advisors recommend diversifying across 2–3 ETFs. Pure-play options like NASA and UFO offer higher upside potential but larger drawdowns, while broader funds like ITA provide more stability.</p>

